---
title: Nonna's Pork Cotoletta & Cherry Tomato Salad with Dill-Parsley Mayo
description: This pork cotoletta is extra special, with our garlic & herb seasoning cooked right into the cheesy crumb! It doesn’t need fancy accompaniments, a fresh tomato and balsamic salad is the perfect pairing. You’ll be thanking Nonna for sharing her best kept culinary secrets.
